latestIgtvVideos.title: Explaining Influencer Marketing in Hindi!!!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Today marks ONE year of 1. doing this influencer thing full time and 2. trying to figure how I was gonna make a legit income from this!

And to celebrate this journey (which I have a long loooong way to go), kicking off the #BehindEveryInfluencer series. As with any goal of mine, it’s been 10 fold more important to me to share the behind the scenes of what worked and what didn’t, so we can continue to grow together. 

“Yeh influencer marketing hai kya?” is a question I’ve been asked a COUNTLESS number of times, especially from my grandparents and their friends, so if you’ve been 1. asked this or 2. need to explain why you wanna do this, HERE YA GO!! 

Comment below what questions you have and will try my best to make it happen!

had no clue THIS was the room we were getting!!! my notes on @kirinisantorini —

✨both of us loooove a good breakfast spread and we honestly ate so much that we skipped lunch most days! on request, the chef made fresh hash browns and got me all the chopped up ingredients to make my cream cheese-tomato-green chili toasts haha. would plan on a 1-1.5 hour meal since you order a la carte vs being able to grab from a buffet and leave for your day. all the servers are extremely kind, hospitable and always remembered our drink orders from the morning before!!

✨location was a 10-12 min walk from the heart of oia which was perfect for what we were looking for. super romantic, amazing views, not loud. this probably goes for any hotel property in oia, but there are a lot of steps to get to your room and around the property. would factor that in accordingly. 

✨ask for dimitris at the spa - shyam claims it was one of the best massages of his life lol.

all in all would def recommend this property for a luxurious honeymoon or couple’s trip! and shoutout to @americanexpress platinum for getting us the upgrade!!

i’ve been to a lot of shows, but nothingggg like this!!! def bookmark @thegreekweddingshow for your trip to santorini! 🇬🇷❤️

👉🏼 ticket cost includes appetizers (all vegetarian) and wine (if you drink) that they serve during the performance, so you can nibble while they’re singing / dancing. 

👉🏼 the show is set as if you’re a relative attending a greek family wedding and they do such an amazing job of involving the entire audience!!

👉🏼 great for all ages! it’s a 2 hour show and you really get to experience a taste of greek culture, music and dance. 

💡 and what’s been on my mind since… WE NEED AN INDIAN VERSION OF THIS SHOW!!! maybe a @marigolddiaries_ production down the line!!
